OL,3,CChurch leadership say Bishop of
OL,4,CLiverpool 'will need to step aside'
OL,6,FSenior members of the Diocese of
OL,7,FLiverpool have called the current
OL,8,Fposition of the Bishop of Liverpool
OL,9,FJohn Perumbalath "untenable" following
OL,10,Fa number of allegations brought
OL,11,Fagainst him.
OL,13,FAs part of a Channel 4 investigation,
OL,14,Ftwo women accused the Bishop of sexual
OL,15,Fassault and harassment between 2019
OL,16,Fand 2021, before he was enthroned in
OL,17,Fhis current position.
