OL,6,FThe statement was signed Debra Walker,
OL,7,FChair of the House of Laity, Peter
OL,8,FDawkin, Chair of the House of Clergy,
OL,9,FSue Jones, Dean of Liverpool, Pete
OL,10,FSpiers, Archdeacon of Knowsley &
OL,11,FSefton, Miranda Threlfall-Holmes,
OL,12,FArchdeacon of Liverpool, and Simon
OL,13,FFisher, Archdeacon of St Helens and
OL,14,FWarrington.
OL,16,FBishop Perumbalath said he has
OL,17,F"consistently denied" the allegations
OL,18,Fand complied with any investigation
OL,19,Ffrom the National Safeguarding Team
OL,20,F(NST).
